Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:16.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは ｷﾝ肉ﾏﾝが 残虐超人を\N倒すために 使用した技です｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:16.10,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,The Kinniku Buster was used by Kinnikuman to destroy the evil super humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｷﾝ肉ﾏﾝが ごつい超人相手に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.58,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I cannot imagine that Kinnikuman had perverted intentions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:20.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやらしい目的で\N使用していたとは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:21.36,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,when using this move against the giant super humans.
