Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.87,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,should be the Hasegawa Buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長谷川ﾊﾞｽﾀｰ というのが 正しい！
